conbody.p: (a) Copies of the TAR in Federal Register, and CFR form may be purchased from the Superintendent of Documents, Government Printing Office, Washington, DC 20402. The electronic version of the Federal Register may be found at http://www.nara.gov and the CFR at http://www.gpoaccess.gov.
(b) The (TAR) 48 CFR chapter 12 and Transportation Acquisition Circulars (TACs) are available on the Internet at http://www.dot.gov/ost/m60.
